<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Slime" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Slime,</orth> viscous mire; any glutinous substance: <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.126" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 126</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.3.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 3, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.7.25" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.355" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 355</bibl>. <cit><quote>hates the s. that sticks on filthy deeds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.148" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 2, 148</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>